## Notes
- model.py has been patched for compatibility with newer torch-geometric
- aggr is now passed to super().__init__() instead of propagate()
- add_self_loops() return value unpacked as tuple
- edge_index.long() cast added before propagate()
- If regenerating embeddings, ensure SMILES strings match exactly with LANCE dataset JSON